{"tid":1956762,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"高盛料4月底美國領失業金人數升至1800萬","createTime":"2020-04-03T11:46:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T13:50:17.000Z","uid":3302,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a14a05464a4f25c3ca6ad2fbf657cf14567ac4d1","tid":1956762,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T11:46:16.000Z","msg":"高盛報告指，美國上星期新申領失業救濟人數反映，美國企業裁員速度急劇加快，估計稍後公布的上月失業率將升至3.8%，上月非農業就業人數將下降18萬人，多於市場預期的10萬人。<br />\n<br />\n高盛指，失業救濟人數申請數據，將是評估美國經濟衰退深度，以及何時開始復蘇的指標。報告預計，新申領失業救濟人數未來數周仍會非常高，至4月底，將有近1800萬人超額申請，相當於對實際經濟造成12%的衝擊。<br />\n<br />\n報告又預期，包括紐約和西雅圖在內的大城市，受新型肺炎疫情拖累較大，預料餐飲服務、住宿、消閒服務、社會援助等行業的私人薪酬，將會顯著減少。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1518739-20200403.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1518739-20200403.htm&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2BhYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=7964a522\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1518739-20200403.htm&h=58a686f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1518739-20200403.htm</a>"},{"pid":"50f9fdccdfb0b89f690fd0df79f6dd637219dfac","tid":1956762,"uid":25952,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T11:48:16.000Z","msg":"中國真係令全球人類食晒屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0403f3f5229d9388530b33edcd29e01849df20bb","tid":1956762,"uid":51920,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"50f9fdccdfb0b89f690fd0df79f6dd637219dfac","tid":1956762,"uid":25952,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T11:48:16.000Z","msg":"中國真係令全球人類食晒屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T11:49:53.000Z","msg":"班美國佬自己唔戴口罩走去怪人"},{"pid":"0cf5e8c6d0e6e4e5b946486754600ea17bd80cae","tid":1956762,"uid":210922,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T11:50:18.000Z","msg":"個